WEBVTT

00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:02.656
Black girls as young as seven,

00:12:02.680 --> 00:12:06.400
great grandmothers as old as 95

00:12:07.520 --> 00:12:09.280
have been killed by the police.

00:12:09.960 --> 00:12:12.000
They've been killed in their living rooms,

00:12:12.760 --> 00:12:14.000
in their bedrooms.

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:16.720
They've been killed in their cars.

00:12:17.800 --> 00:12:19.736
They've been killed on the street.

00:12:19.760 --> 00:12:22.616
They've been killed
in front of their parents

00:12:22.640 --> 00:12:25.440
and they've been killed
in front of their children.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.800
They have been shot to death.

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:30.960
They have been stomped to death.